他说他勉勉强强上完小学和中学.

6
00:00:17,513 --> 00:00:19,760
He told me he did really badly at university.
还告诉我他大学读的也不好.

7
00:00:20,221 --> 00:00:22,328
Well,he learned to run a company somewhere.
Well, 他在某个地方学会了经营公司.

8
00:00:22,815 --> 00:00:24,493
He makes a ton of money.
他赚很多钱.

9
00:00:25,239 --> 00:00:25,755
That's the thing.
怪就怪在这里.

10
00:00:26,362 --> 00:00:27,693
He said he was bad at maths.
他说他的数学不好.

11
00:00:28,727 --> 00:00:28,991
At what?
什么不好?

12
00:00:30,274 --> 00:00:30,549
Maths.
数学.

13
00:00:31,664 --> 00:00:32,254
You mean math?
你是说math?

14
00:00:32,792 --> 00:00:33,335
We say maths.
我们说maths.

15
00:00:35,056 --> 00:00:36,631
You must mean all the different maths.
你一定是指各种不同的数学.

16
00:00:36,954 --> 00:00:39,011
Because I mean the one basic math.
因为我指的是最基础的数学.

17
00:00:39,579 --> 00:00:39,857
Whatever.
随便哪个都行.

18
00:00:40,267 --> 00:00:41,289
But Wendy,listen to this.
但是Wendy, 听我说.

19
00:00:41,996 --> 00:00:43,727
He told me making money is easy.
他告诉我赚钱很容易.

20
00:00:44,406 --> 00:00:48,463
He said,"If I buy someting for one dollar,and sell it for two,
他说,"如果我用1美元买一件东西,然后以2美元卖出,

21
00:00:48,996 --> 00:00:51,689
I make money from that one per cent difference."
我就从那百分之一的差价中赚钱."

22
00:00:52,358 --> 00:00:54,703
One per cent?You mean a hundred per cent.
百分之一?你的意思是一百分之一百.

23
00:00:55,579 --> 00:00:59,191
Right.The man can't figure a percentage to save his life.
对. 他就算是为了救命也搞不清楚百分比.

24
00:00:59,765 --> 00:01:00,615
Tell me about it.
你说的没错.

25
00:01:00,998 --> 00:01:02,339
You should see the tip he left me!
你该看看那他留给我的小费!

